%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20Test%20Day%201%3A%20Kohli%2C%20Iyer%20Eye%20Recovery%20For%20India%3B%20Bavuma%20Suffers%20Injury%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIND%20vs%20SA%20Live%20Updates%2C%201st%20Test%20Day%201%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20eye%20recovery%20for%20India%20after%20South%20Africa's%20early%20dominance%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20ongoing%20first%20Test%20in%20Centurion.%20The%20partnership%20between%20Kohli%20and%20Iyer%20has%20crossed%20the%2060-run%20mark%2C%20with%20India%20three%20wickets%20down.%20Rahul%20was%20dismissed%20on%20a%20score%20of%205%2C%20while%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(17)%20too%20got%20out%20for%20cheap.%20Shubman%20Gill%20(2)%20became%20Nandre%20Burger's%20second%20prey.%20Earlier%2C%20South%20Africa%20captain%20Temba%20Bavuma%20had%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bowl.%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20was%20handed%20his%20debut%20for%20India%20while%20Shardul%20Thakur%20also%20get%20the%20nod%20in%20the%20playing%20XI.%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20was%20unavailable%20for%20selection%20due%20to%20an%20upper%20back%20spasm.(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsa-vs-ind-scorecard-live-cricket-score-freedom-trophy-2023-24-1st-test-sain12262023229987%5C%22%3ELive%20Scorecard%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20LIVE%20Updates%20of%201st%20Test%20Match%20Between%20India%20vs%20South%20Africa%2C%20Straight%20from%20Centurion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703586360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7646vvgo_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_26_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Findia-vs-south-africa-live-score-1st-test-day-1-match-today-26-december-ind-vs-sa-match-updates-4743871%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IND%20vs%20SA%20Live%20Updates%2C%201st%20Test%20Day%201%3A%20India%20are%20three%20wickets%20down%20with%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20o