nference%20leader%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20today%20said%20that%20unless%20dialogue%20begins%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20may%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Gaza%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20the%20Srinagar%20MP%20referred%20to%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20statement%20on%20India-Pakistan%20relations%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20can%20change%20our%20friends%20but%20not%20our%20neighbours%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20said%20that%20war%20is%20not%20an%20option%20now%20and%20the%20matters%20should%20be%20resolved%20through%20dialogue.%20Where%20is%20the%20dialogue%3F%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20is%20about%20to%20become%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(of%20Pakistan)%20and%20they%20are%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20talk%20(to%20India)%2C%20but%20what%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20talk%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20do%20not%20find%20a%20solution%20through%20dialogue%2C%20we%20will%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Gaza%20and%20Palestine%2C%20which%20are%20being%20bombed%20by%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0The%20Hamas'%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20and%20the%20brutal%20counterstrike%20that%20followed%20has%20claimed%20over%2021%2C000%20lives%20and%20reduced%20large%20parts%20of%20Gaza%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BAtal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20had%20said%20that%20we%20can%20change%20our%20friends%20but%20not%20our%20neighbours.%20If%20we%20remain%20friendly%20with%20our%20neighbours%2C%20both%20will%20progress.%20PM%20Modi%20also%20said%20that%20war%20is%20not%20an%20option%20now%20and%20the%20matters%20should%20be%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEcPx9B70jJ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEcPx9B70jJ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1739549356267893175%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister's%20remarks%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20series%20of%20unwelcome%20news%20from%20the%20Union%20Territory%20over%20the%20past%20one%20week.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20five%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%20in%20Poonch%2C%20a%20retired%20cop%20was%20shot%20dead%20inside%20a%20Baramulla%20mosque%20and%20three%20civilians%20died%20after%20they%20were%20detained%20by%20troops%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leader%20Dr%20Hina%20Shafi%20Bhat%20has%20criticised%20the%20veteran%20leader's%20remarks%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20regrettable%20that%20a%20senior%20leader%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20still%20talking%20about%20talks%20with%20Pakistan.%20%26quot%3BFarooq%20saab%20should%20learn%20now%2C%20this%20regime%20is%20not%20going%20to%20bow%20down%20before%20Pakistan.%20We%20tried%2C%20they%20have%20backstabbed%20us%20again%20and%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20trashed%20the%20ruling%20BJP's%20claims%20of%20normalcy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20since%20its%20special%20status%20was%20revoked%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShouting%20normalcy%20or%20propagating%20tourist%20arrivals%20as%20peace%20will%20not%20finish%20terrorism.%20They%20were%20claiming%20that%20terrorism%20has%20finished%20with%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20(in%202019)%20but%20four%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20terrorism%20is%20still%20there%20and%20will%20not%20finish%20till%20we%20try%20to%20understand%20its%20root%20cause%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20regret%20the%20killing%20(of%20the%20officer).%20Those%20who%20are%20claiming%20normalcy%20are%20silent...%20they%20tried%20to%20heal%20the%20wounds%20in%20a%20superficial%20manner%20rather%20than%20addressing%20the%20root%20cause.%20The%20commoners%20should%20understand%20that%20we%20are%20losing%20our%20soldiers%2C%20officers%20and%20commoners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20president%20said%20the%20Centre%20needs%20to%20find%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20perspective%26quot%3B%20to%20end%20bloodshed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20part%20of%20India%2C%20we%20were%20part%20of%20India%20and%20we%20will%20remain%20part%20of%20India%20and%20if%20we%20have%20to%20end%20terrorism%2C%20we%20have%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20rather%20than%20claiming%20normalcy%20or%20talking%20about%20tourism%20which%20is%20fragile%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20military%20or%20police%20is%20not%20going%20to%20finish%20terrorism%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20go%20deeper%20and%20address%20the%20root%20cause%20to%20finish%20it%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTerrorists%20attacked%20and%20martyred%20our%20brave%20soldiers%2C%20and%20later%20three%20locals%20were%20tortured%20to%20death.%20This%20is%20tragic%20as%20we%20are%20fighting%20against%20terrorism%20and%20not%20against%20our%20own%20people.%20If%20we%20annoy%20our%20people%2C%20we%20will%20never%20win%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20had%20showed%20willingness%20to%20enter%20into%20dialogue%20with%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20had%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20against%20anyone%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Islamabad%20is%20ready%20to%20talk%20to%20neighbours%20because%20%26quot%3Bwar%20is%20no%20more%20an%20option%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20had%20said%20India%20wants%20neighbourly%20ties%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20there%20should%20be%20an%20atmosphere%20free%20from%20terror%20and%20violence%20for%20such%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20reports%20regarding%20the%20comments%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20PM%20on%20this%20issue.%20India's%20clear%20and%20consistent%20position%20is%20well%20known%20that%20we%20desire%20normal%20relations%20with%20all%20our%20neighbouring%20countries%20including%20Pakistan.%20For%20this%20environment%20free%20of%20terror%20and%20hostility%20is%20imperative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703583720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fafuc9m3_farooq-abdullah-sings-jeena-yahan-marna-yahan-at-parliament-complex_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullah-on-india-pakistan-dialogue-if-no-talks-we-will-meet-same-fate-as-gaza-palestine-4744435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Criticising%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20for%20not%20talking%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20resolve%20disputes%2C%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20today%20said%20that%20unless%20dialogue%20begins%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20may%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Gaza%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullah-on-india-pakistan-dialogue-if-no-talks-we-will-meet-same-fate-as-gaza-palestine-4744435%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullah-on-india-pakistan-dialogue-if-no-talks-we-will-meet-same-fate-as-gaza-palestine-4744435%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullah-on-india-pakistan-dialogue-if-no-talks-we-will-meet-s