Cp%3EPeople%20have%20come%20from%20Texas%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20UK.%20Even%20New%20Yorkers.%20Some%20come%20on%20multiple%20tours.%20It's%20really%20cool%20to%20meet%20people%20from%20all%20around%20the%20world%20that%20you%20would%20have%20never%20met%20just%20because%20of%20a%20rat%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20different%20things%20people%20see.%20Rats%20in%20garbage%20bags%2C%20rats%20running%20across%20people's%20feet%20when%20they%20don't%20know%20they're%20there.%20Rats%20scaring%20people%2C%20people%20love%20that.%20Rats%20climbing%20up%20street%20signs%20and%20trying%20to%20jump%20into%20trash%20cans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPeople%20get%20their%20phones%20out%20like%20they're%20in%20Jurassic%20Park%20or%20something%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22tiktok%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40nyc_kb%2Fvideo%2F7283921415403818286%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227283921415403818286%5C%22%20data-embed-from%3D%5C%22oembed%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40nyc_kb%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%40nyc_kb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40nyc_kb%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrash%20cans%20won%E2%80%99t%20solve%20the%20rat%20problem%20when%20they%20are%20overflowing%20or%20can%E2%80%99t%20close%20because%20there%20is%20no%20container.%202023%20and%20New%20York%20still%20is%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20throw%20away%20trash.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fnycratczar%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22nycratczar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23nycratczar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fnycrats%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22nycrats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23nycrats%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href