ople%20don't%20really%20do%20because%20rats%20carry%20diseases%20and%20all%20kinds%20of%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20like%20rats.%20In%20New%20York%20City%2C%20they're%20not%20pets.%20They're%20pests.%20That's%20what%20I%20try%20to%20explain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPeople%20call%20me%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20names%20on%20TikTok%2C%20but%20'Rat%20Daddy'%20is%20the%20main%20one%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20it%20for%20entertainment%20but%20also%20to%20bring%20awareness.%20Sometimes%20rats%20look%20cute%20in%20the%20videos%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20they're%20not%20cute%20when%20they're%20chewing%20down%20your%20restaurant%20or%20infesting%20places.%20They%20cause%20damage%20to%20businesses.%20A%20rat%20could%20be%20inside%20your%20business%20and%20give%20you%20a%20bad%20restaurant%20grade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20whole%20myriad%20of%20things%20that%20we%20talk%20about%20on%20the%20livestreams%20and%20tours%2C%20like%20how%20New%20Yorkers%20can%20mitigate%20the%20situation%20by%20closing%20trash%20can%20bins%20and%20not%20putting%20trash%20on%20the%20sidewalk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tour%20starts%20at%2010%3A30%20a.m.%20We%20begin%20at%20Grand%20Central%2C%20and%20then%20we%20go%20to%20the%20news%20store%2C%20which%20is%20infested%20with%20mice.%20I%20always%20tell%20people%20that's%20the%20appetizer.%20Then%20we%20walk%20around%20Pershing%20Square%2C%20down%20to%20Third%20Avenue%20and%20back%20toward%2042nd%20Street.%20There%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20stops%20on%20the%20way%20that%20we'll%20see%20rats%20100%25%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20number%20of%20rats%20we%20see%20does%20depend%20on%20the%20weather.%20Usually%2C%20when%20it's%20raining%2C%20you%20won't%20see%20too%20many.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20it's%20cold%20or%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20rats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20I%20study%20where%20they%20go%20to%20and%20from%20their%20nest%20so%20I%20know%20we're%20not%20in%20the%20direct