.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fbharatpe-earns-rs-904-cr-against-a-loss-before-tax-of-rs-886-cr-in-fy23-123122600412_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fbharatpe-earns-rs-904-cr-against-a-loss-before-tax-of-rs-886-cr-in-fy23-123122600412_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar%20Explains%20Why%20'INDIA'%20Doesn't%20Need%20PM%20Face%20With%20A%201977%20Example%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20proposed%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20candidate%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20veteran%20politician%20Sharad%20Pawar%20struck%20a%20different%20note%2C%20saying%20that%20projecting%20a%20face%20for%20the%20top%20post%20makes%20no%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20comes%20amid%20political%20posturing%20by%20INDIA%20members%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20when%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20will%20take%20on%20the%20formidable%20BJP.%20The%20posturing%20intensified%20after%20the%20Congress%2C%20projecting%20itself%20as%20the%20big%20force%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%20three%20heartland%20polls.%20So%20now%2C%20while%20Opposition%20leaders%20project%20a%20united%20front%2C%20regional%20rivalries%20continue%20to%20be%20at%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20in%20Pune%20yesterday%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20chief%20was%20asked%20about%20INDIA%20not%20having%20a%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%20In%20reply%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20went%20back%20to%20the%201977%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20after%20Emergency%20when%20the%20Janata%20Party%20scored%20a%20thumping%20victory%20against%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%201977%20elections%2C%20no%20