mmunity%20member%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20untouchability%20was%20banned%20after%20Independence%2C%20members%20of%20the%20dominant%20caste%20conjured%20up%20a%20story%20to%20perpetuate%20the%20practice%2C%20saying%20that%20a%20voodoo%20doll%20has%20been%20buried%20under%20the%20street%20and%20if%20SC%20people%20walked%20on%20the%20street%20with%20slippers%2C%20they%20will%20die%20within%20three%20months.Some%20SC%20members%20believed%20those%20stories%20and%20started%20walking%20without%20slippers%2C%20and%20the%20practice%20continued%20to%20this%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Untouchability%20Eradication%20Front%20(Tiruppur)%20secretary%20CK%20Kanagaraj%20visited%20the%20village%20last%20week%20and%20found%20that%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fdec%2F26%2F60-dalits-walk-with-slippers-on-upper-caste-street-end-years-of-scourge-in-tn-village-2644949.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBy%2520doing%2520so%252C%2520they%2520broke%2CNaickers%252C%2520a%2520Backward%2520Caste%2520community.%5C%22%3EDalit%20women%20were%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20enter%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20particular%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outfit%20wanted%20to%20launch%20a%20protest%20but%20the%20police%20refused%20permission%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20postpone%20it.%20Subsequently%2C%20members%20of%20the%20front%20along%20with%20functionaries%20of%20political%20parties%20like%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20Viduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%2C%20and%20Dalit%20rights%20organisation%20Aathi%20Thamizhar%20Peravai%20decided%20to%20walk%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2060-member%20group%20then%20entered%20Rajakaliamman%20temple%20in%20the%20village%20which%20has%20remained%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20Dalits%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fd