e%20village%20reportedly%20stormed%20Sangita%E2%80%99s%20house.%20According%20to%20Ram%20Kapi%2C%20the%20husband%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%20the%20attackers%20interrupted%20Sangita%20while%20she%20was%20cooking%20and%20physically%20assaulted%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThey%20branded%20her%20as%20a%20witch%20and%20beat%20her%20up.%20I%20requested%20them%20to%20not%20beat%20her%20and%20come%20in%20the%20morning.%20I%20was%20also%20beaten%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kapi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fdec%2F26%2Fwitch-hunt-tribal-woman-burnt-alive-2645007.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20pleas%20for%20them%20to%20stop%20and%20return%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20the%20assailants%20continued%20their%20brutal%20attack%20on%20Sangita.%20Ram%20was%20also%20beaten%20up%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20intervene%20and%20save%20Sangita.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fdec%2F26%2Fwitch-hunt-tribal-woman-burnt-alive-2645007.html%5C%22%3Epolice%20have%20arrested%20six%20individuals%3C%2Fa%3E%20believed%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20attack.%20The%20suspects%2C%20all%20residents%20of%20the%20same%20village%2C%20are%20currently%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20awaiting%20further%20legal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Assam%20has%20one%20of%20the%20most%20stringent%20laws%20against%20witch-hunting%2C%20yet%20instances%20of%20women%20being%20chased%20away%20or%20killed%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20being%20witches%20still%20surface%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Assam%20government%20data%2C%20between%202011%20and%202019%2C%20107%20people%20were%20killed%20across%20the%20state%20in%20witch-hunting%20inc