uld%20be%20the%20guiding%20motto%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20farthest%20from%20their%20thoughts%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20latest%20sign%20is%20the%20case%20of%20Australian%20batter%20Usman%20Khawaja%20who%20was%20barred%20from%20wearing%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%20is%20a%20human%20right%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Call%20lives%20are%20equal%E2%80%9D%20on%20his%20shoes%20during%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Perth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThank%20you%20to%20all%20those%20who%20supported%20and%20gave%20me%20love%20this%20week.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20unnoticed%20%F0%9F%92%95.%20Nothing%20worthwhile%20is%20easy.%20History%20shows%20we%20are%20doomed%20to%20repeat%20the%20mistakes%20of%20our%20past.%20But%20together%20we%20can%20fight%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20%F0%9F%99%8F%F0%9F%8F%BE%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Ffreedomisahumanright%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23freedomisahumanright%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Falllivesareequal%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23alllivesareequal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHAhbebDbCT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHAhbebDbCT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Usman%20Khawaja%20(%40Uz_Khawaja)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUz_Khawaja%2Fstatus%2F1736680713657999851%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20had%20also%20copped%20a%20reprimand%20for%20having%20sported%20a%20black%20armband%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20Test%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20at%20Perth%20Stadium%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20ICC%20has%20gone%20further%20and%20rejected%20his%20application%20to%20spread%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20by%20sporting%20a%20dove%20with%20an%20olive%20branch%20on%20his%20shoe%20during%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20Article%20One%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%20that%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20human%20beings%20are%20born%20free%20and%20equal%20in%20dignity%20and%20rights.%20They%20are%20endowed%20with%20reason%20and%20conscience%20and%20should%20act%20towards%20one%20another%20in%20a%20spirit%20of%20brotherhood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhawaja%2C%20who%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20his%20beliefs%2C%20has%20the%20support%20of%20his%20cricket%20board%2C%20his%20captain%20Pat%20Cummins%20and%20teammates.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20really%20support%20Uzzy%20(Khawaja).%20I%20think%20he%E2%80%99s%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20he%20believes%2C%20and%20I%20think%20he%E2%80%99s%20doing%20it%20really%20respectfully%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20at%20a%20presser%2C%20Cummins%20argued%20that%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20Usman%20Khawaja%20displaying%20a%20dove%20logo%20on%20his%20shoe%20and%20bat%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20humanitarian%20issues%20and%20teammate%20Marnus%20Labuschagne%20displaying%20an%20eagle%20on%20his%20bat%20which%20signifies%20a%20personal%20religious%20message.%20Labuschagne%20displays%20the%20symbol%20of%20an%20eagle%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20bats%20which%20represents%20a%20verse%20from%20the%20bible%20and%20has%20long%20been%20allowed%20to%20have%20the%20sticker%20on%20his%20bat%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20player%20in%20the%20Australian%20team%2C%20including%20Khawaja%2C%20also%20have%20multiple%20advertising%20stickers%20on%20their%20bats%20that%20represent%20different%20companies%20including%20their%20bat%2Fequipment%20sponsor%20and%20a%20secondary%20personal%20sponsor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20religious%20cause%20is%20acceptable%2C%20commercial%20gain%20is%20welcomed%20but%20a%20message%20for%20peace%20and%20humanity%20is%20not.%20The%20message%20is%20about%20Gaza%20where%20Israeli%20military%20action%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20including%208%2C000%20children.%20Khwaja%20is%20not%20wearing%20a%20Palestinian%20symbol%20or%20an%20Islamic%20motif.%20He%20is%20reminding%20the%20world%20of%20what%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%2C%20adopted%20after%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hypocrisy%20of%20those%20who%20constantly%20shouted%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20again%E2%80%9D%20and%20pledged%20to%20uphold%20the%20%E2%80%9Crules-based%20global%20order%E2%80%9D%20is%20laid%20bare%20by%20this%20simple%20gesture%20by%20Khwaja.%20It%20is%20way%20short%20of%20what%20was%20done%20to%20Russian%20athletes%20after%20Putin%20invaded%20Ukraine%3B%20or%20when%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20wore%20camouflage%20pattern%20caps%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20ICC%20should%20feel%20uncomfortable%20with%20Khwaja%E2%80%99s%20request%20is%20hard%20to%20comprehend.%20Cricket%20is%20a%20game%20mainly%20played%20by%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20barring%20England%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20where%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20has%20overwhelming%20support.%20South%20Africa%20and%20Ireland%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20those%20speaking%20against%20the%20horrors%20being%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%20India%20is%20the%20outlier%20here%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20has%20embraced%20the%20US%20position%20rather%20closely%20and%20supported%20his%20friend%20Bibi%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20is%20sending%20Indian%20workers%20to%20replace%20the%20Palestinian%20labour%20working%20in%20the%20construction%20sector%20in%20Israel.%20His%20supporters%20remain%20in%20thrall%20of%20an%20Islamophobic%20narrative%2C%20which%20is%20reinforced%20by%20the%20Israeli%20state%20narrative%20about%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20party%20is%20a%20staunch%20supporter%20of%20Israel%20and%20avoids%20asking%20for%20peace%20and%20justice%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20occupied%20areas.%20It%20controls%20the%20BCCI%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20spiritual%20and%20material%20boss%20of%20the%20ICC.%20Is%20that%20the%20reason%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20request%20has%20been%20denied%20by%20the%20ICC%3F%20What%20else%20could%20be%20the%20reason%3F%20Meanwhile%2C%20here%20in%20India%2C%20forget%20current%20or%20former%20cricketers%2C%20even%20sports%20journalists%20are%20unwilling%20to%20underline%20the%20Khawaja%20episode%20lest%20it%20forces%20people%20to%20wonder%20why%20Indian%20cricket%20superstars%20are%20such%20cowards%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%20subjugated%20into%20submission%20by%20those%20who%20now%20have%20parasitic%20control%20over%20Indian%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20for%20the%20ICC%2C%20peace%20and%20brotherhood%20is%20too%20much%20to%20ask%20for.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20cricket.%20Neither%20is%20it%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESushant%20Singh%20is%20Senior%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703571621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26114543%2FUntitled-design-14-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-usman-khawaja-icc-bcci-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20for%20the%20ICC%2C%20peace%20and%20brotherho