ere%20allowed%20to%20leave%20after%20brief%20interrogation%20by%20the%20CISF%20officials%2C%20others%20are%20still%20being%20questioned.%20A%20charter%20plane%2C%20with%20276%20passengers%20on%20board%2C%20landed%20at%20Mumbai's%20Chattrapati%20Shivaji%20International%20Airport%20in%20the%20wee%20hours%20on%20Tuesday.%20On%20leaving%20the%20airport%20after%20arriving%20from%20France%2C%20passengers%20tried%20their%20best%20to%20avoid%20queries%20from%20the%20waiting%20media.%20The%20aircraft%2C%20which%20was%20ground%20by%20French%20authorities%20last%20week%2C%20was%20headed%20to%20Nicaragua.%20The%20flight%2C%20with%20303%20passengers%2C%20was%20headed%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Nicaragua.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhuman-trafficking-scam-cisf-interrogates-indian-passengers-deported-from-france%2Farticleshow%2F106282863.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRam%20In%20My%20Heart%2C%20No%20Need%20To%20Show%20Off%26quot%3B%3A%20Kapil%20Sibal%20On%20Ram%20Temple%20Invite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%20has%20said%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20in%20his%20heart%20and%20he%20does%20not%20need%20to%20engage%20in%20any%20show%2C%20the%20statement%20came%20when%20Mr%20Sibal%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20intends%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20at%20Ayodhya%20scheduled%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20Ram%20in%20my%20heart.%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20show%20off.%20What%20I%20say%20to%20you%20is%20from%20my%20heart%20because%20I%20do%20not%20care%20about%20all%20these%20things.%20If%20Ram%20is%20in%20my%20heart%20and%20Ram%20has%20guided%20me%20throughout%20my%20journey%2C%20it%20means%20that%20I%20have%20done%20something%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20speaking%20to%20ANI%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Congress%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20whole%20Ram%20Mandir%20construction%20issue%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bshow%20off%26quot%3B%20because%20the%20ruling%20party's%20behaviour%2C%20character%20are%20nowehere%20similar%20to%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20whole%20issue%20is%20a%20show-off.%20They%20(BJP)%20talk%20about%20Ram%20but%20their%20behaviour%2C%20their%20character%20are%20nowhere%20close%20to%20Ram's.%20Truthfulness%2C%20tolerance%2C%20sacrifice%2C%20and%20respect%20for%20others%20are%20some%20of%20the%20traits%20of%20Ram%20but%20they%20do%20exactly%20the%20opposite.%20They%20say%20they%20are%20constructing%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20are%20glorifying%20Ram%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20politician%20said%20that%20one%20needs%20to%20have%20Lord%20Ram's%20principles%20in%20one's%20heart%20and%20fulfil%20the%20constitutional%20goals%20following%20his%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20in%20your%20heart%20is%20not%20Ram.%20You%20need%20to%20have%20Ram's%20principles%20in%20your%20heart%20and%20fulfil%20the%20constitutional%20goals%20by%20following%20his%20principles%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapil%20Sibal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20newly%20passed%20criminal%20bills%20in%20Parliament%2C%20Sibal%20said%20that%20they%20are%20more%20rigorous%20than%20the%20'colonial'%20ones%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20any%20'Indian-ness'%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20these%20bills%20were%20passed%2C%20I%20think%20that%20our%20constitutional%20institutions%20should%20not%20have%20passed%20the%20bills%20in%20this%20manner.%20You%20suspended%20100%20people%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%2046%20people%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20And%20when%20this%20bill%20was%20discussed%20in%20the%20committee%2C%20we%20requested%20them%20to%20consult%20eminent%20lawyers%20for%20these%20bills%20but%20they%20chose%20to%20go%20with%20their%20leaders.%20Then%20they%20b