s%20that%20they%20are%20capturing%20the%20civil%20services!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20who%20has%20any%20career%20these%20days%2C%20except%20the%20rich!%20Our%20boys%20are%20going%20around%20doing%20%3Cem%3Edeshbhakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20streets.%20Their%20boys%20are%20protesting.%20Achcha%2C%20first%20you%20change%20the%20channel.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20see%20this%20stupid%20man%20while%20I%20am%20eating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20brought%20out%20the%20rotis%20from%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20Aamna%20is%20worried%20about%20Jamal.%20Their%20only%20son!%20He%20could%20easily%20have%20gone%20abroad.%20Aamna%20was%20talking%20about%20him%20at%20the%20party%20office%20yesterday%2C%20and%20didi%20said%20to%20us%20that%20our%20children%20are%20too%20sensitive%20for%20the%20present%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20children%20are%20sensible%20also%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20sensitive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20was%20coughing%20fitfully%20when%20Amma%20flung%20open%20the%20door%20to%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHide%20in%20your%20room%20and%20have%20more%20cigarettes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20air.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmma%20rolled%20her%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20that%20Achche%20bhai%20is%20like%20a%20brother%20to%20me.%20Pushpa%20and%20I%20are%20like%20sisters.%20You%20insulted%20him%20in%20public%3F%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20hear%20any%20excuses.%20Get%20up%20right%20now%2C%20go%20and%20bring%20rotis%20from%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20shop.%20Achche%20bhai%20will%20come%20for%20lunch%20and%20you%20will%20apologise%20to%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20swatted%20at%20a%20single%20fly%20and%20managed%20to%20kill%20two.%20He%20was%20really%20quite%20large%2C%20but%20always%20underestimated%20his%20own%20str