r%20to%20his%20right%2C%20barked%2C%20%E2%80%9CBring%20Jamal%20bhai%E2%80%99s%20packets!%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20observed%20him%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20and%20enquired%20casually%3A%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20hennaed%20your%20beard%2C%20Laadley%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20Khan%20blushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slightly%20built%20man%2C%20wearing%20a%20checked%20lungi%20and%20a%20sleeveless%20brown%20sweater%2C%20was%20hunched%20over%20the%20clay%20oven.%20He%20got%20up%20silently%20and%20handed%20Jamal%20a%20stack%20of%20greasy%20brown%20paper%20packets%20that%20smelled%20of%20tandoori%20roti%20and%20kabab.%20Jamal%20leaned%20back%20as%20he%20adjusted%20them%20against%20his%20chest.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20love%20of%20Allah%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20have%20the%20place%20swept%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99d%20very%20much%20like%20to%20have%20the%20place%20swept%2C%20Jamal%20bhai%2C%20but%20what%20will%20I%20do%20with%20the%20trash%3F%20The%20municipal%20cart%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20all%20the%20way%20here%2C%20does%20it%3F%20Every%20bastard%20is%20turning%20vegetarian%20suddenly.%20Nobody%20wants%20to%20touch%20animal%20filth%2C%20it%20seems.%20Not%20even%20the%20thieving%20%3Cem%3Emehtars%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%E2%80%99d%20have%20the%20waste%20thrown%20into%20the%20municipal%20dump%20on%20the%20main%20road%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99d%20just%20lie%20there%20also%2C%20and%20then%20everyone%20will%20get%20upset%20with%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20say%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20my%20garbage%2C%20let%20it%20just%20stay%20here.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchcha%3F%20And%20what%20will%20people%20think%20when%20they%20come%20to%20eat%20your%20nehari%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20comes%20to%20eat%20my%20nehari%3F%20Everyone%20buys%20rotis%20from%20me%20and%20then%20goes%20to%20Rahman%20Miyan%E2%80%99s%20fancy%20restaurant%20to%20eat%20his%20famous%20paya.%20All%20the%20big%20people%20go%20there%2C%20and%20the%20foreigners%20too.%20Only%20some%20local%20friends%20like%20you%20and%20Habib%20bhai%20come%20here%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20there%20is%20no%20obligation%20on%20you%20to%20keep%20your%20shop%20clean%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COho%20Jamal%20bhai.%20Locals%20are%20more%20troublesome%2C%20I%20must%20say.%20Arrey%2C%20the%20Angrez%20are%20simple%20people.%20They%20come%20here%20to%20see%20the%20old%20city%2C%20eat%20nehari%2C%20not%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20garbage.%20Do%20you%20know%2C%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20a%20%3Cem%3Efirangi%3C%2Fem%3E%20came%20to%20my%20shop%3F%20He%20had%20been%20walking%20around%20the%20old%20city%20and%20he%20came%20here%20for%20lunch%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20a%20word%20about%20the%20rubbish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20minions%20nodded%20in%20agreement%3A%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20the%20firangi%20was%20very%20cultured.%20He%20folded%20his%20hands%20and%20said%20%3Cem%3Enamaste%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3B%20everyone%20cackled%20at%20the%20firangi%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20faux%20pas%20and%20Jamal%20grinned%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20our%20Mullah%20ji%2C%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20even%20tried%20to%20correct%20him.%20He%20said%20sternly%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EWe%3C%2Fem%3E%20say%20salaam%20aleikum%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20poor%20man%20got%20very%20confused.%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20clapped%20his%20thighs%20in%20mirth%20and%20the%20assistants%20continued%20to%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Jamal%20had%20left%20the%20shop%20with%20his%20packets%2C%20Laadley%20Khan%20turned%20towards%20the%20tandoor%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CListen%2C%20swine%2C%20collect%20this%20rubbish%20now%20and%20throw%20it%20into%20the%20dump.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20see%20this%20mess%20in%20front%20of%20my%20shop.%E2%80%9D%20The%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%20appeared%20largely%20unaffected%2C%20so%20Laadley%20Khan%20continued%20to%20glower%20at%20him%2C%20his%20mouth%20slightly%20open%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20right%3F%20You%20heard%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20I%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20front%20of%20my%20juniors%2C%20he%20said%20that%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20I%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20being%20a%20wastrel.%20That%20I%20was%20a%20jihadi%2C%20and%20a%20bad%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsghar%20and%20Aamna%20sat%20next%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20divan%2C%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20not%20laugh..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20said%20you%20are%20a%20Jihadi.%20I%20did%20say%20you%20are%20wasting%20your%20time.%20Your%20father%20retired%20from%20the%20examination%20section%20at%20Jamia.%20He%20has%20helped%20so%20many%20people%20from%20your%20community%20in%20getting%20pass%20marks.%20But%20his%20own%20son%20is%20now%20failing%20his%20exams.%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20stopped%20for%20a%20quick%20breadth%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20you%20just%20look%20at%20your%20health!%20Who%20gets%20sugar%20at%20your%20age%3F%20And%20even%20then%20you%20are%20not%20being%20careful.%20His%20friend%20was%20saying%20that%20because%20of%20his%20sugar%20he%20suddenly%20gets%20angry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsghar%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20to%20intervene.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20apologise%20to%20your%20chacha.%20Achche%20has%20carried%20you%20on%20his%20shoulders%20at%20so%20many%20of%20our%20rallies.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20dare%20presume%20to%20teach%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPushpa%20carried%20him.%20I%20was%20usually%20on%20duty%20by%20the%20time%20he%20was%20born.%20Of%20course%20in%20our%20student%20days%20we%20went%2C%20but%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20born%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20%3Cem%3Ehe%3C%2Fem%3E%20went%20to%20rallies%20as%20a%20student%2C%20then%20it%20was%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20grumbled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20times%20are%20different%20now.%20When%20we%20held%20rallies%2C%20it%20was%20for%20nation%20building%2C%20not%20for%20anti-national%20things.%20There%20were%20no%20hidden%20agendas%2C%20no%20international%20funding%20and%20toolkits%20to%20brainwash%20people%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20get%20arrested%20and%20then%20my%20parents%20would%20go%20crying%20to%20him%20for%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20we%20would%20go%20to%20him%20for%20help.%20One%20asks%20ones%20closest%20family%20only%20for%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Aamna.%20%E2%80%9CStop%20arguing%20with%20your%20chacha.%20Go%20put%20the%20rotis%20out.%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20unfolded%20his%20legs%20and%20reluctantly%20rose%20from%20his%20seat.%20She%20waited%20for%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20room%20and%20then%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CAchche%20bhai%2C%20you%20also%20start%20arguing%20as%20if%20you%20were%20the%20same%20age%20as%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20at%20all%20acting%20his%20age.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20tell%20him%20to%20get%20into%20some%20government%20department%2C%20preferably%20the%20police%20force.%20He%20would%20be%20able%20to%20help%20himself%20and%20his%20community%20much%20better%20that%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20your%20right%20and%20your%20duty%20to%20point%20him%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20Achche.%20But%20tell%20me%20frankly%2C%20how%20many%20Muslims%20are%20there%20in%20your%20own%20thana%3F%20How%20many%20SHOs%20are%20Muslim%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Asghar%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20you%20have%20to%20at%20least%20try%20to%20get%20into%20the%20system.%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20said%20irritably.%20He%20later%20told%20Pushpa%20that%20they%20are%20becoming%20too%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20becoming%20negative%3F%20Asghar%20bhai%2C%20or%20the%20entire%20Muslim%20community%3F%E2%80%9D%20Pushpa%20laughed.%20%E2%80%9CMore%20important%2C%20did%20you%20ask%20Jamal%20to%20come%20home%20on%20Diwali%3F%20He%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20him%20separately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20sat%20on%20a%20wooden%20bench%2C%20which%20was%20chained%20to%20the%20collapsible%20grill%20of%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar.%20The%20shop%20had%20sold%20crisp%20kachauris%20and%20jalebis%20and%20milky%20tea%20since%201949.%20The%20boys%20had%20been%20rocking%20the%20bench%20when%20Shambhu%2C%20the%20owner%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20came%20rushing%20out%20and%20yelled%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20do%20that!%20You%E2%80%99ll%20break%20the%20bench.%20Anyway%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20meant%20for%20patrons%2C%20not%20for%20freeloaders%20to%20lounge%20on.%E2%80%9D%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20in%20mild%20embarrassment%20and%20Kanwal%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20have%20some%20tea%2C%20in%20that%20case.%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20muttered%20something%20under%20his%20breath%20and%20went%20back%20into%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoss%2C%20it%20is%20not%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nirmal%20to%20Kanwal.%20%E2%80%9DWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20sit%20anywhere%20in%20peace.%20Constantly%20have%20to%20be%20buying%20something.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20westernisation%2C%20boss.%20Western%20consumerism%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kanwal%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20right.%20In%20the%20old%20days%20people%20could%20sit%20anywhere%3B%20they%20would%20be%20offered%20tea.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sense%20of%20%3Cem%3Eatithi%20devo%20bhava%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20no%20pride%20in%20our%20culture%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Nirmal%20stopped%20mid-sentence%2C%20and%20nudged%20Kanwal%3A%20%E2%80%9CBoss%2C%20see%20what%20he%20is%20doing!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slightly%20built%20man%20wearing%20a%20checked%20lungi%20and%20sleeveless%20sweater%20had%20emptied%20a%20bucket%20just%20outside%20the%20low%20boundary%20of%20the%20municipal%20dump.%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20could%20make%20out%20several%20bones%20and%20some%20gristle%20in%20the%20heap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEh%2C%20what%20do%20you%20think%20you%E2%80%99re%20doing%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kanwal%20shouted%20from%20across%20the%20road.%20The%20man%20looked%20startled%2C%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond.%20He%20turned%20nervously%20and%20made%20to%20go%20back%20into%20the%20alley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20been%20butchering!%E2%80%9D%20Nirmal%20yelled.%20The%20fleeing%20man%20stopped%20and%20turned%20around%20abruptly%3A%20%E2%80%9CAbey%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20mataji.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20a%20goat.%20Can%E2%80%99t%20you%20tell%20from%20the%20size%20of%20the%20bones%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20left%20their%20place%20on%20the%20bench%20and%20ran%20across%20the%20street%2C%20but%20they%20stopped%20at%20the%20head%20of%20the%20alley%20and%20glanced%20at%20each%20other%20hesitantly.%20Kanwal%20hated%20going%20into%20that%20filthy%20alley%2C%20where%20they%20slaughtered%20animals%20and%20left%20their%20bloodied%20organs%20strewn%20about%20as%20if%20to%20mock%20him.%20If%20he%20could%2C%20he%20would%20have%20driven%20them%20all%20out.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Barbarians%2C%20terrorists!%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%20he%20spat%20in%20disgust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmal%20looked%20at%20his%20friend%20for%20encouragement%20and%20shouted%20at%20the%20man%2C%20who%20had%20stopped%20at%20a%20safe%20distance%20inside%20the%20alley%3A%20%E2%80%9CPick%20up%20your%20filth%20and%20take%20it%20back%20inside!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20the%20municipal%20dump!%E2%80%9D%20the%20man%20shouted%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20meant%20for%20butchers%20and%20savages.%20Take%20it%20back%20or%20we%E2%80%99ll%20slaughter%20you%20and%20sprinkle%20your%20bones%20in%20the%20dump.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruckus%20grew%2C%20and%20the%20noise%20reached%20Laadley%20Khan%20in%20his%20nehari%20shop.%20He%20stepped%20out%20curiously%2C%20as%20did%20several%20of%20his%20customers%2C%20forming%20a%20crowd%20behind%20him.%20Amongst%20them%20was%20Salman%2C%20the%20local%20delinquent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20going%20on%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20threw%20the%20waste%20into%20the%20dump%20just%20as%20you%20told%20me%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%20started%20chasing%20me%20and%20abusing%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20slightly%20built%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20go%20inside.%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20Khan%20said%20to%20him%2C%20and%20then%20turned%20towards%20Kanwal%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaan%20bhai%3F%20What%20is%20the%20problem%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20for%20encouragement%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20allow%20desecration%20of%20our%20land%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20dump%20is%20your%20land%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20no%20animal%20slaughter%20in%20our%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%2C%20his%20feet%20wide%20apart%20and%20arms%20akimbo%2C%20frowned%20exaggeratedly%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20his%20audience%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20area%3F%C2%A0%20How%20is%20this%20your%20area%3F%20Your%20sister%20is%20married%20to%20Srivastava%20ji%E2%80%99s%20son.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20come%20from%20some%20village%20to%20live%20in%20your%20sister%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20study%2C%20and%20this%20has%20become%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20area%3F%20My%20ancestors%20are%20buried%20here%20%E2%80%93%20permanently%20%E2%80%93%20not%20like%20you.%E2%80%9D%20The%20rearguard%20hooted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20regarded%20Laadley%20Khan%20with%20distaste.%20He%20wore%20a%20filthy%20shalwar-kameez%2C%20with%20the%20shalwar%20tied%20high%20and%20reaching%20his%20ankles.%20He%20also%20had%20a%20ridiculous%20henna-coloured%20beard%2C%20which%20provoked%20Kanwal%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20country%20is%20ours.%20You%20can%20go%20to%20Pakistan%20if%20you%20want!%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20and%20made%20as%20if%20to%20charge.%20Nirmal%20held%20him%20back%20and%20said%2C%20pacifyingly%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20our%20people%20win.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20then%20put%20them%20all%20in%20a%20municipal%20cart%2C%20with%20all%20the%20rubbish%2C%20and%20send%20them%20where%20they%20belong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20looked%20gleeful%20as%20he%20readied%20himself%20for%20a%20fight.%20There%20were%20catcalls%20from%20his%20customers%20and%20his%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20drunk%20your%20mother%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20come%20here%20and%20fight!%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20pumped%20his%20chest%20and%20called%20out.%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%2C%20who%20were%20poised%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20alley%2C%20yelled%20back%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20come%20out%20some%20time%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20you%3F%20We%E2%80%99ll%20show%20you%20then.%20We%20remember%20all%20your%20faces%2C%20you%20bastards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAm%20I%20scared%20of%20you%2C%20you%20little%20twerp%3F%E2%80%99%20Laadley%20Khan%20roared%20as%20he%20started%20to%20walk%20towards%20them.%20At%20that%20fortuitous%20moment%2C%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20of%20Thana%20Sadar%20appeared%20at%20the%20junction%20of%20the%20road%20and%20alley%2C%20followed%20closely%20by%20Jamal%2C%20whose%20parents%20had%20insisted%20that%20he%20walk%20Achche%20chacha%20to%20the%20auto%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%3F%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20asked%20sternly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20you%20only%20said%20to%20throw%20away%20the%20garbage.%20I%20told%20you%20the%20municipal%20cart%20never%20comes%20into%20our%20gali%2C%20and%20when%20we%20throw%20garbage%20on%20the%20main%20road%2C%20then%20these%20people%20throw%20tantrums.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20doing%20this%20to%20provoke%20us.%20He%20is%20showing%20us%20slaughtered%20animals!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kanwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20that%20offend%20you%20suddenly%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20turned%20to%20look%20at%20the%20heap%20that%20had%20been%20deposited.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20inside%20the%20dump%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20emptied%20it%20on%20the%20street%2C%20literally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20inside%20only%2C%E2%80%9D%20whimpered%20the%20slightly%20built%20man%20from%20within%20the%20alley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20got%20a%20toehold%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWho%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20thrown%20all%20this%20outside%20the%20designated%20spot%3F%20Hup%2C%20come%20here!%E2%80%9D%20he%20barked%20at%20the%20slightly%20built%20man.%20The%20man%20retreated%20further%20into%20the%20dark%20recesses%20of%20the%20alley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20throws%20it%20there.%20If%20you%20throw%20it%20close%20enough%20to%20the%20dump%2C%20everyone%20understands%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20garbage.%20And%20anyway%2C%20why%20did%20they%20have%20to%20go%20prodding%20to%20look%20at%20what%20was%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20Khan%20scowled%20back.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20say%20anything%20to%20those%20two%20troublemakers%2C%20Inspector%20saheb%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20I%20arrest%20you%20only%20Laadley%3F%20We%20have%20to%20first%20investigate%20whether%20there%20has%20been%20any%20illegal%20slaughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20snapped%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%20chacha%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20say%20such%20things.%20It%20is%20a%20sensitive%20matter.%20If%20you%20say%20it%20lightly%20even%2C%20people%20will%20believe%20it%20to%20be%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20whispered%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EChaliye%2C%20aap%20log%20bhi%20chaliye%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20pointed%20his%20chin%20at%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%20Then%20he%20gestured%20towards%20the%20alley%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20letting%20them%20be%20because%20of%20you%20Jamal%2C%20otherwise%20one%20or%20two%20deserve%20to%20be%20in%20jail.%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20glanced%20at%20Laadley%2C%20but%20let%20his%20eyes%20rest%20on%20Salman.%20He%20then%20took%20a%20few%20quick%20strides%20and%20left%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20began%20walking%20back%20towards%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar.%20Shambhu%20had%20come%20out%20of%20the%20shop%2C%20and%20was%20watching%20them%20with%20admiration.%20Halfway%2C%20they%20stopped%20again%2C%20turned%20around%20and%20yelled%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20get%20boys%20from%20the%20university%3B%20they%E2%80%99ll%20teach%20you%20to%20hurt%20peoples%E2%80%99%20sentiments%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20break%20all%20your%20bones%2C%20you%20scoundrel.%20They%20have%20been%20sent%20here%20to%20study%2C%20but%20all%20they%20do%20is%20create%20trouble%20and%20waste%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20yelled%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20say%2C%20Laadley%20bhai%2C%20they%20are%20just%20frustrated%20because%20they%20are%20single.%20All%20the%20frustration%20is%20coming%20out%20like%20this.%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20have%20them%20blessed%20at%20the%20dargah%2C%20they%20might%20find%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%20Salman%20called%20out%20and%20the%20crowd%20tittered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20flared%20up%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20have%20us%20blessed%3F%20You%20fiend!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20portly%20Balabhadra%20babu%20owned%20a%20Xerox%2C%20scanning%20and%20printing%20shop%20in%20the%20bazaar%2C%20his%20previous%20enterprise%20in%20cyber%20cafes%20having%20failed%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20smartphones.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20was%20an%20affable%20man%3A%20early%20on%20in%20his%20printing%20career%2C%20he%20had%20landed%20a%20profitable%20contract%20for%20printing%20%E2%80%98Modi%20masks%E2%80%99%20for%20distribution%20at%20election%20rallies.%20He%20had%20made%20good%20money%20but%20even%20better%20contacts%20and%20had%20gone%20on%20to%20benefit%20greatly%20from%20that%20distinguished%20visage.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20had%20printed%20Covid%20vaccination%20certificates%2C%20posters%20felicitating%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20grand%20success%2C%20and%20most%20recently%2C%20banners%20announcing%20the%20forthcoming%20inauguration%20of%20the%20grand%20temple%2C%20and%20once%20again%20commending%20the%20honourable%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20was%20usually%20clad%20in%20starched%20kurtas%20and%20pyjamas%2C%20which%20acquired%20a%20dirty%20blue%20tinge%20from%20excessive%20use%20of%20Neel%20in%20the%20wash.%20He%20was%20sipping%20tea%20at%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar%20that%20evening.%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20were%20on%20the%20opposite%20bench%2C%20talking%20softly%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20always%20carried%20an%20air%20of%20sanguinity%20about%20him.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20are%20you%20young%20people%20discussing%2C%20hain%3F%20You%20are%20young%20men%2C%20you%20should%20devote%20time%20to%20nation%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20somewhat%20superfluously%2C%20to%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmal%20had%20been%20sitting%20with%20one%20leg%20folded%20under%20him%2C%20while%20the%20other%20dangled%20off%20the%20ground.%20Excitedly%2C%20he%20unfolded%20his%20leg%20and%20stood%20up%3A%20%E2%80%9CBulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20we%20%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%20work%20together.%20Our%20attitude%20should%20be%20nation%20first%3B%20everything%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20for%20minorities%20and%20backwards%20alone%2C%20while%20meritorious%20and%20nationalist%20youth%20suffer.%20We%20cannot%20allow%20this%20policy%20of%20appeasement%20any%20longer%2C%20and%20open%20cow%20slaughter%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKanwalji%20and%20Nirmalji%20suspect%20that%20Laadley%20has%20slaughtered%20a%20cow.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20catch%20them%20red-handed%2C%20but%20they%20have%20given%20him%20a%20strict%20warning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20explained.%20Their%20status%20at%20the%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar%20had%20evidently%20changed%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20intervention.%20He%20shook%20his%20head%20resolutely%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20it%2C%20Kanwal%2C%20but%20not%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20certain%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nirmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20here%2C%20They%20do%20it%2C%20I%20am%20aware.%20But%20not%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20about%20these%20things%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha.%20Come%20we%E2%80%99ll%20show%20you%20the%20bones%2C%20then%20you%20can%20decide%20for%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20put%20his%20half-finished%20glass%20of%20tea%20down%20and%20got%20up%20without%20a%20word.%20He%20followed%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20to%20the%20municipal%20dump%20across%20the%20street%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Shambhu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20other%20patrons%20from%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20they%20stood%20in%20a%20semi-circle%20trying%20to%20look%20for%20the%20gristle%20and%20the%20bones.%20Much%20more%20garbage%20had%20been%20piled%20on%20since%20the%20incident%20in%20the%20morning.%20Nirmal%20found%20a%20long%20stick%20and%20prodded%20the%20trash%20till%20they%20found%20the%20gristle.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20gathered%20the%20back%20of%20his%20kurta%20and%20sat%20down%20on%20his%20haunches%20to%20observe%20the%20bones%20more%20closely.%20He%20smiled%20in%20relief%20and%20shook%20his%20head%3A%20%E2%80%9DGoat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20look%20at%20the%20size!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9DBig%20goat%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20He%20paused%2C%20and%20then%20added%20reassuringly%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20easy%20transporting%20animals%20into%20that%20narrow%20alley.%20We%20are%20all%20here%20watching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20had%20also%20gathered%20his%20friends%20that%20evening%20for%20a%20discussion%20of%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20events.%20As%20they%20put%20out%20the%20clay%20oven%2C%20he%20had%20said%20to%20the%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%2C%20%E2%80%9CArre%20if%20we%20catch%20Jamal%20bhai%20in%20a%20good%20mood%2C%20he%20will%20lift%20your%20spirits!%20Why%20do%20you%20always%20look%20so%20sad%20and%20scared%20you%20rascal%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20lit%20himself%20a%20cigarette%2C%20took%20a%20long%20drag%20and%20coughed%3A%20%E2%80%9CThen%20Laadley%3F%20This%20has%20been%20good%20for%20your%20business%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbey%2C%20your%20little%20fight%20with%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal!%20They%20have%20declared%20that%20they%20saw%20you%20slaughter%20right%20here%20and%20everyone%20believes%20it.%20I%20heard%20someone%20say%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20go%20searching%20for%20good%20kababs%20anymore%2C%20when%20our%20Laadley%20is%20here.%20Now%20you%20can%20raise%20your%20prices%20again%20and%20continue%20to%20serve%20dog%20meat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20touched%20his%20earlobes%20with%20the%20tip%20of%20his%20fingers%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no%2C%20tauba%20Jamal%20bhai.%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20do%20such%20a%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20okay.%20But%20it%20is%20true%20about%20the%20dogs%20though%2C%20what%20do%20you%20say%20Habibi%3F%20He%20peddles%20dog%20meat%20as%20mutton.%20Have%20you%20noticed%20how%20dogs%20run%20for%20cover%20when%20they%20see%20Laadley%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20seemed%20delighted%20at%20the%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20when%20there%20are%20no%20dogs%20left%2C%20he%20goes%20after%20crows.%20Have%20you%20noticed%20how%20there%20are%20no%20crows%20in%20our%20area%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20pinched%20his%20earlobes%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20all%20you%20say%20Jamal%20bhai!%20But%20by%20God%2C%20do%20you%20know%20the%20poultry%20shops%20in%20chowk%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20looked%20around%20at%20his%20audience%2C%20%E2%80%9CHain%3F%20They%20get%20these%20sickly%20local%20quails%20and%20colour%20them%20all%20neela-peela%2C%20and%20then%20sell%20them%20at%20double-price%20saying%20they%20are%20migratory%20birds%20and%20have%20only%20fed%20on%20Irani%20and%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20on%20the%20way.%20And%20people%20buy%20them%20also!%E2%80%9D%20Everyone%20burst%20into%20peals%20of%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20door%20opened%20and%20shut%20loudly%2C%20nearby%2C%20and%20Salman%20teetered%20into%20the%20alley%2C%20looking%20flushed%2C%20brushing%20his%20hair%20with%20the%20back%20of%20his%20hand.%20He%20came%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20stairs%20at%20a%20respectable%20distance%20from%20Jamal%20and%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKya%20hero%3F%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20half-witted%20husband%20is%20out%20again%20tonight%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20blushed%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%20rolled%20over%20with%20laughter.%20%E2%80%9CAbey%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20fall%20into%20the%20tandoor!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%2C%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20really%20love%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20caused%20Laadley%20Khan%20to%20guffaw%20so%20much%20that%20his%20belly%20shook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20quickly%20changed%20the%20subject%3A%20%E2%80%9CLaadley%20bhai%2C%20you%20stopped%20me%2C%20otherwise%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20let%20those%20two%20get%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20did%20I%20stop%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20always%20that%20the%20police%20are%20biased.%20If%20it%20were%20just%20%3Cem%3Ethem%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20problem%2C%20but%20who%20can%20fight%20with%20the%20police%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%2C%20sheepishly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20was%20not%20biased%20today.%20Inspector%20Achche%20Lal%20contained%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20both%20of%20you%20are%20finding%20fault%20with%20everything%20I%20say.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabib%20sighed.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20everyone%20so%20angry%20all%20the%20time%3F%20First%2C%20Jamal%20bhai%20had%20a%20fight%2C%20then%20Laadley%20had%20a%20fight%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20all%20become%20radicalised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20cackled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20foreign%20hand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20smiled%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20Nirmal%20and%20Kanwal%20have%20had%20an%20awakening%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20Rahman%20miyan%20only%20who%20has%20encouraged%20this%20kind%20of%20activity%20in%20our%20area.%20He%20has%20brought%20the%20police%20in%20and%20now%20swine%20like%20Nirmal%20and%20Kanwal%20feel%20they%20can%20question%20us.%20Earlier%2C%20would%20anyone%20have%20dared%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20looked%20accusingly%20at%20Salman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20has%20he%20brought%20the%20police%20in%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Habib%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre!%20He%20is%20a%20daily%20informer.%20Tattles%20on%20everyone.%20Who%20said%20what%3F%20Who%20did%20what%3F%20Even%20the%20poor%20children%20in%20his%20madarsa%20%E2%80%93%20everyone%20is%20under%20scrutiny.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20spat%20dramatically.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20informed%20on%20all%20the%20anti-CAA%20protestors.%20So%20many%20had%20to%20go%20to%20jail.%20Everyone%20hates%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20Romeo%20also%20got%20into%20trouble.%20Rahman%20miyan%20has%20thrown%20him%20out%20of%20his%20quarters%20at%20the%20madarsa.%