%2C%20the%20surveillance%20on%20public%20meetings%2C%20protest%20marches%2C%20and%20rallies%20have%20tightened%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20such%20changes%20are%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20responses%20of%20British%20society%20and%20politics%20to%20the%20anti-war%20campaign%20Britain%20has%20been%20witnessing%20for%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20Since%20the%20second%20week%20of%20October%2C%20Britain%20has%20virtually%20returned%20to%20the%20days%20of%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20wars%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20a%20couple%20of%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20Saturday%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fgallery%2F2023%2F10%2F29%2Fhundreds-of-thousands-march-worldwide-against-israeli-bombardment-of-gaza%5C%22%3Eare%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20order%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpro-palestine-protesters-disrupt-oxford-street-christmas-shoppers-in-call-to-boycott-pro-israel-brands-13036859%5C%22%3Eoppose%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fdec%2F23%2Fprotest-in-oxford-street-london-calls-for-gaza-ceasefire-and-boycott-of-brands%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20military%20offensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gaza.%20People%20are%20also%20holding%20marches%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fworld%2Fthousands-rally-world-support-of-israel-palestine-8983038%2F%5C%22%3Esupport%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20albeit%20of%20a%20much%20smaller%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Corbyn%20has%20become%20the%20face%20of%20pro-Palestine%20protests%2C%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Boris%20Johnson%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2023%2Fnov%2F05%2Fboris-johnson-and-scott-morrison-join-forces-on-solidarity-trip-to-israel%5C%22%3Epro-Israel%20marches%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Incidents%20like%20anti-war%20demonstrations%20in%20front%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%20a%20demonstration%20of%20social%20activists%20inside%20the%20parliament%20premises%2C%20protests%20outside%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Labour%20leader%20Keir%20Starmer%20characterise%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20time.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20current%20Palestine%20crisis%20has%20come%20to%20take%20the%20centrestage%20in%20British%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%5C%22%3EThe%20Israel-Palestine%20War%20Is%20a%20Stain%20on%20Every%20One%20of%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20Big%20Brother%20USA%2C%20the%20entire%20British%20%E2%80%98political%20establishment%E2%80%99%20has%20openly%20sided%20with%20Israel.%20While%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20visited%20Israel%20to%20convey%20his%20message%20of%20solidarity%20to%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20the%20current%20Labour%20leader%20(widely%20perceived%20as%20the%20would-be%20prime%20minister)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6275507%2Fkeir-starmer-interview-uk%2F%5C%22%3ESir%20Keir%20Starmer%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20similar%20stand.%20Things%2C%20however%2C%20started%20changing%20since%20October%2014%2C%20when%20several%20organisations%2C%20including%20Stop%20the%20War%20Coalition%20and%20the%20Palestine%20Solidarity%20Campaign%2C%20convened%20a%20pro-Palestine%20protest%20march%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20gathering%20of%20over%20150%2C000%20people.%20Corbyn%20was%20the%20only%20British%20MP%20to%20attend%20this%20very%20first%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20subsequently%2C%20the%20attendance%20in%20these%20weekly%20protest%20marches%20continued%20to%20surge%2C%20reaching%20over%20800%2C000%20in%20the%20fourth%20march%20since%20October%207.%20This%20is%20being%20accompanied%20by%20the%20growing%20participation%20of%20MPs%2C%20social%20activists%2C%20and%20trade%20union%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20in%20street%20demonstrations%20has%20already%20exerted%20enough%20pressure%20on%20British%20political%20parties%20of%20every%20stripe%2C%20and%20especially%2C%20the%20Labour%20Party.%20While%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20Britain%20has%20traditionally%20been%20a%20Labour%20constituency%2C%20Sir%20Keir%E2%80%99s%20stand%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20favour%20has%20caused%20widespread%20discontent%20among%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20committed%20Muslim%20voters.%20The%20impact%20has%20been%20felt%20within%20the%20party%20as%20well.%20More%20than%20a%20hundred%20Labour%20councillors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2Foct%2F16%2Flabour-councillors-quit-party-in-protest-at-keir-starmers-israel-stance%5C%22%3Ehave%20already%20resigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20protest%20against%20Sir%20Keir%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20Israel.%20In%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-67435955%5C%22%3E56%20Labour%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20against%20the%20Labour%20leader%E2%80%99s%20stand%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Moreover%2C%20at%20least%2010%20members%20of%20his%20shadow%20cabinet%20have%20openly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2Foct%2F25%2Flabour-party-divisions-israel-gaza-starmer%5C%22%3Eopposed%20his%20views%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Starmer%20has%20never%20faced%20such%20a%20strong%20opposition%20within%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Tories%20could%20not%20also%20escape%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20anti-war%20campaign.%20In%20a%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20opinion%20piece%2C%20Suella%20Braverman%2C%20the%20former%20Home%20Secretary%20and%20the%20most%20vocal%20Tory%20leader%20against%20the%20pro-Palestine%20protesters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2Fnov%2F08%2Fsuella-braverman-accuses-police-of-double-standards-on-rallies%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20of%20playing%20%E2%80%9Cfavourites%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20protesters%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20being%20tougher%20on%20right-wing%20extremists.%20She%20even%20requested%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20police%20to%20impose%20a%20ban%20on%20pro-Palestine%20marches.%20The%20Metropolitan%20Police%2C%20however%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20oblige%2C%20as%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20grave%20law-and-order%20problem%20by%20banning%20protests%20involving%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20people.%20Following%20this%20development%2C%20Sunak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frishi-sunak-suella-braverman-david-cameron%5C%22%3Ereplaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Braverman%20with%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20David%20Cameron%2C%20who%20is%20known%20as%20a%20centre-right%20politician%20in%20the%20Conservative%20Party.%20The%20ruling%20Conservatives%2C%20thus%2C%20are%20also%20caught%20up%20in%20this%20whirlwind%20caused%20by%20the%202023%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20these%20two%20larger%20parties%2C%20the%20Liberal%20Democrats%20%E2%80%93%20the%20second%20choice%20of%20the%20British%20Muslims%20after%20the%20Labour%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20have%20also%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20war.%20Due%20to%20the%20pressure%20of%20its%20Muslim%20and%20leftist%20members%2C%20the%20party%20has%20supported%20the%20ceasefire.%20Lib%20Dem%20members%20could%20even%20be%20seen%20in%20anti-war%20marches%20with%20their%20banners.%20The%20wide%20participation%20of%20trade%20unions%2C%20which%20in%20Britain%20include%20workers%20of%20all%20political%20colours%2C%20has%20also%20added%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20anti-war%20campaign.%20Most%20of%20the%20trade%20unions%20including%20the%20RMT%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20trade%20union%20covering%20the%20transport%20sector%20%E2%80%93%20Unite%20the%20Union%2C%20and%20the%20UNISON%20have%20taken%20part%20in%20pro-Palestine%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20Britain%20has%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20around%20pro-Palestine%20and%20anti-war%20activism.%20While%20Corbyn%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-65102128%5C%22%3Eexit%20from%20the%20Labour%20leadership%3C%2Fa%3E%20signalled%20a%20huge%20setback%20for%20the%20British%20Left%2C%20they%20are%20now%20gaining%20fresh%20steam%20due%20to%20these%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fgallery%2F2023%2F10%2F20%2Fphotos-palestine-solidarity-rallies-around-the-world%5C%22%3Eprotest%20marches%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20characterised%20by%20their%20diversity%2C%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20flags%20being%20waved%20at%20them.%20Immigrants%20from%20various%20countries%20march%20with%20their%20respective%20national%20flags%2C%20while%20protesters%20display%20flags%20representing%20socialist%20nations%20like%20Cuba%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Venezuela%2C%20and%20Brazil.%20Additionally%2C%20former%20Soviet%20Union%20flags%20can%20be%20seen%20alongside%20the%20Palestinian%20flag.%20Supporters%20of%20the%20Kurdistan%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Party%20carry%20their%20own%20flags%2C%20and%20flags%20of%20the%20Tudeh%20Party%20of%20Iran%20and%20the%20Iranian%20People%E2%80%99s%20Fedai%20Guerrillas%20stand%20alongside%20those%20of%20the%20Palestine%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party.%20Expatriate%20members%20of%20the%20PFLP%2C%20a%20communist%20guerrilla%20organisation%20in%20Palestine%2C%20proudly%20march%20with%20their%20distinctive%20red%20flags.%20Even%20supporters%20of%20Erdogan%20participate%2C%20waving%20the%20Turkish%20national%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20the%20African%20Left%20in%20these%20demonstrations%20is%20highly%20noticeable.%20Members%20of%20the%20South%20African%20Communist%20Party%20march%20alongside%20their%20counterparts%20from%20the%20Marxist-Leninist%20EFF.%20Women%20from%20Kenya%2C%20Mali%2C%20and%20Zimbabwe%20are%20visible%2C%20holding%20anti-racist%20banners%20advocating%20for%20the%20unity%20of%20women%20of%20colour.%20Jews%20join%20the%20march%20with%20a%20banner%20boldly%20saying%20%E2%80%98Not%20in%20our%20name.%E2%80%99%20Furthermore%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20diaspora%20actively%20participate%20in%20each%20protest%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-jewish-voice-for-peace-apartheid%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20in%20Our%20Name%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Jews%20Who%20Refuse%20to%20Be%20Bystanders%20to%20Historic%20Injustice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20big%20question%20is%3A%20why%20are%20such%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20people%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20London%20to%20support%20Palestine%3F%20Aren%E2%80%99t%20they%20working%20in%20favour%20of%20Hamas%3F%20When%20I%20asked%20this%20question%20to%20Corbyn%2C%20the%20old%20man%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20at%20all.%20This%20huge%20crowd%20is%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20against%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20cleansing%20in%20the%20name%20of%20fighting%20Hamas%2C%20against%20the%20slaughter%20of%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20including%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20all%2C%20it%20was%20Hamas%20who%20started%20the%20war%20on%20October%207.%20Corbyn%E2%80%99s%20answer%20was%20clear%20enough%3A%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20tell%20me%20that%20anti-colonial%20violence%20was%20started%20by%20the%20freedom%20fighters%20of%20India%20or%20Africa%3F%20Similarly%2C%20this%20war%20was%20not%20started%20by%20Hamas%20or%20the%20PLO.%20While%20the%20October%207%20violence%20should%20be%20condemned%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20carrying%20on%20with%20its%20occupation%20in%20Palestine%20since%201948%20and%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20an%20unfortunate%20response%20to%20that.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20eradicate%20the%20fundamental%20reason%20behind%20this%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20unjust%20occupation%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20such%20bold%20arguments%20will%20also%20face%20counter-arguments%2C%20the%20Palestine%20crisis%20will%20not%20move%20off%20the%20centrestage%20of%20British%20politics%20for%20some%20time%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703501902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25160650%2Fimage-1667.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-israel-palestine-war-is-shifting-the-political-dynamics-in-britain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20line%20with%20the%20US%2C%20the%20entire%20British%20%E2%80%98political%20establishment%E2%80%99%20has%20openly%20sided%20with%20Israel.%20Conversely%2C%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20surge%20in%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20led%20by%20diverse%20groups%2C%20with%20the%20stance%20on%20the%20conflict%20causing%20discontent%20within%20political%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-israel-palestine-war-is-shifting-the-political-dynamics-in-britain%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20join%20huge%20migrant%20caravan%20in%20Mexico%20ahead%20of%20Blinken%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703497976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F13B99%2Fproduction%2F_132139708_screenshot2023-12-25011629.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67818686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20group%20set%20off%20just%20days%20before%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken's%20visit%20to%20Mexico%20City.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A350%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http