the%20Israeli%20state%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20attacks%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%E2%80%99s%20Manger%20Square%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20full%20of%20visitors%20and%20tourists%20around%20Christmas%20time%20%E2%80%93%20is%20desolate%20this%20year.%20No%20festive%20lights%20have%20been%20put%20up.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20city%20is%20empty%20from%20happiness%2C%20from%20joy%2C%20from%20kids%2C%20from%20Santa.%20There%20is%20no%20celebration%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madeleine%2C%20a%20Bethlehem%20resident%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67815370%5C%22%3Etold%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20priest%20at%20the%20Nativity%20Church%2C%20Father%20Eissa%20Thaldjiya%2C%20echoed%20Isaac%E2%80%99s%20sentiments.%20He%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20he%20has%20never%20seen%20a%20Christmas%20like%20this%20before%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20celebrate%E2%80%A6%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20be%20united%20in%20prayers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChristmas%20is%20joy%2C%20love%20and%20peace.%20We%20have%20no%20peace.%20We%20have%20no%20joy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Father%20Spiridon%20Sammour%2C%20a%20Greek%20Orthodox%20priest%20at%20the%20Church%20of%20the%20Nativity%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F24%2Fmiddleeast%2Fbethlehem-christmas-gaza-war-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20out%20of%20our%20hands%2C%20and%20we%20pray%20for%20the%20leaders%20who%20will%20make%20the%20decisions%20%5Ball%5D%20over%20the%20world%20to%20God%20to%20help%20them%2C%20give%20them%20his%20light%20to%20make%20peace%20here%20and%20all%20over%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChurch%20leaders%20in%20Jerusalem%20too%20have%20spoken%20out%20against%20the%20Israeli%20state%E2%80%99s%20